B.af_=new A.jD("The core scripture verses of the Bhagavad Gita are recognized as public domain material. However, the custom UI compilation, software container code, visual themes, custom layouts, engineering logic, and original architectural content are the exclusive proprietary property of Satvik Technologies.",null)
