B.af3=new A.jD('This application structure is delivered to the endpoint user on an "As-Is" and "As-Available" baseline without warranties of any variety, either express or implied. Satvik Technologies and its single-member community administration shall bear zero legal or financial liability for any specific choices, conclusions, or actions initiated by you based on the metrics or text processed inside the app.',null)
